# TodoApp API Plan

## Planned Endpoints
* GET /users
* GET /users/{id}
* POST /users
* PUT /users/{id}
* DELETE /users/{id}
* GET /groups
* GET /groups/{id}
* POST /groups
* PUT /groups/{id}
* DELETE /groups/{id}
* GET /roles
* GET /roles/{id}
* POST /roles
* PUT /roles/{id}
* DELETE /roles/{id}
* GET /todos
* GET /todos/{id}
* POST /todos
* PUT /todos/{id}
* DELETE /todos/{id}
## Request/Response Conventions
* JSON requests and responses
## Validation Rules
* Validate user input
## Error Response Conventions
* Return error messages in JSON format
## Authentication Requirements
* JWT authentication required for all endpoints